'''玛纳卡玛纳庙'''（[[天城文|天城文]]{{lang-ne|मनकामना मन्दिर}}，拉丁文转写：Manakamana Mandir），位于[[尼泊尔|尼泊尔]][[甘达基专区|甘达基专区]][[廓尔喀县|廓尔喀县]]，是一座[[印度教|印度教]]寺庙。<ref name="Sacred Sites">{{cite web|title=Sacred Sites, places of peace and power|url=http://sacredsites.com/asia/nepal/manakamana.html|accessdate=December 15, 2012|archive-date=2015-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150315192904/http://sacredsites.com/asia/nepal/manakamana.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==简介==
该寺庙主供巴格瓦蒂（[[雪山女神|雪山女神帕尔瓦蒂]]的化身）。<ref name="Sacred Sites"/>“玛纳卡玛纳”一名来自两个词：“mana”意思是“心”，“kamana”意思是“希望”。该寺从17世纪起受到崇奉。

该寺庙位于廓尔喀县以南12公里。<ref>{{cite web|title=Dakshinkali and Manakamana temple|url=http://www.enepalholidays.com/pilgrimage-tours/dakshinkali-and-manakamana-temple-tours.php|access-date=2015-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150526045825/http://www.enepalholidays.com/pilgrimage-tours/dakshinkali-and-manakamana-temple-tours.php|archive-date=2015-05-26|dead-url=yes}}</ref>海拔1302米，俯瞰其南侧的特里苏利河（Trisuli）以及其西侧的马相迪河（Marsyangdi）。从[[加德满都|加德满都]]开车大约104公里可到达该寺。从[[博克拉|博克拉]]乘坐公共汽车3到4个小时也可到达。<ref name="Cable car ride">{{cite web|title=Cable car ride|url=http://www.ghalegroup.com/tripDetail/132/44/1/Cable-Car-Ride.html|accessdate=December 15, 2012|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120724154319/http://www.ghalegroup.com/tripDetail/132/44/1/Cable-Car-Ride.html|archivedate=2012-07-24|deadurl=yes}}</ref>

2015年4月25日，[[2015年尼泊尔地震|尼泊尔发生强烈地震]]，该寺庙倒塌。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://rt.com/news/252965-earthquake-nepal-india-damage |title=At least 4 killed, dozens trapped after 7.9-magnitude earthquake strikes Nepal (PHOTOS, VIDEO) |accessdate=2015-04-25 |work=RT |publisher= |date= |archive-date=2015-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150425133905/http://rt.com/news/252965-earthquake-nepal-india-damage/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

